<!-- ///  begin faq  /// -->
<div class="faq" id="faqSection">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4 wow fadeInLeft">
        <h1>FAQ</h1>
        <hr>
        <p>Here are the answers to some common questions about InviroConnect! If you don't find the answer you're looking for, please fill out the form <a href='#home'>above</a> for more information.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-8 wow fadeInRight">
        <div class="panel-group" id="faq">
          <div class="panel">
            <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#faq" href="#faq1">
              Who can use InviroConnect?
            </a>
            <div id="faq1" class="panel-collapse collapse">
              <p>InviroConnect works with lots of different people wanting to come together for the Earth. We especially encourage you to set up an account if you are a university student, a nonprofit, a government agency, or a business interested in supporting environmental causes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="panel">
            <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#faq" href="#faq2">
              How do I sign up?
            </a>
            <div id="faq2" class="panel-collapse collapse">
              <p>InviroConnect is still in the development phase right now, but we expect it to be launched by January of 2016. Fill out the form <a href='#home'>here</a> if you'd like us to contact you when the full site is online. Be sure to note if you'd like to be considered as a beta tester!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="panel">
            <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#faq" href="#faq3">
              What is your pricing model?
            </a>
            <div id="faq3" class="panel-collapse collapse">
              <p>In order to have our customers pay the smallest amount possible, we aren't announcing pricing until the site is more fully implemented. We are committed to keeping the cost of participation very affordable. Please <a href='#home'>contact us</a> if you'd like us to let you know when more information is available.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="panel">
            <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#faq" href="#faq4">
              What locations does InviroConnect serve?
            </a>
            <div id="faq4" class="panel-collapse collapse">
              <p>Our pilot region is Oregon. However, we intend to expand into other areas as well. If you aren't in Oregon, please <a href='#home'>contact us</a> and ask us to keep you in the loop!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="panel">
            <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#faq" href="#faq5">
              Can this be used to organize for other causes?
            </a>
            <div id="faq5" class="panel-collapse collapse">
              <p>You will be able to do that in the future, but right now, InviroConnect is focusing on environmental issues, because they're what we know best.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>                
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
